#include <cstdio>

using namespace std;

bool ispower10(int n)
{
	if(n == 1 || n == 10 || n == 100 || n == 1000 || n == 10000 || n == 100000)
		return true;
	return false;
}

int main()
{
	int t;
	scanf("%d",&t);
	while(t--)
	{
		int n;
		scanf("%d",&n);
		if(ispower10(n))
			printf("NO\n");
		else
			printf("YES\n");
	}
	return 0;
}
